snippet.title: Tell The World / JUSTICE FOR JOHNNY
snippet.description:
Whilst  #AmberHeard had released her evidence that stained Johnny's image, Johnny had released a lot of evidence too which should result in a similar or even worse fate for Amber heard who had lied, been abusing the #MeToo system, brought on a hoax, spread offensive tweets or text messages as 'jokes'. She claimed she didn't want anything except for a divorce from Johnny and yet made a huge demand list. 
There is too much evidence such as pictures, witnesses and medical statements which prove to be in Johnny's favour - he is a victim of DV.
This is nothing to do with genders, a woman shouldn't strike a man just like a man shouldn't strike a woman. 
I stand with Justice. I stand with Johnny Depp.
Along with the rest of a line of plenty of DV victims.
 #AbuseHasNoGender
 #MenToo

Also, I support  #JohnnyDepp, I guess I am a bot lol
